PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Finance of Frederick W. Gorbet, of Ottawa, Ontario, as a director of the Board of Directors of Petro-Canada Limited to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Helen Meyer, whose term has expired.
